data.description: DREAM HOME ON NEAR LAKE LIVINGSTON! This lovely home stands out among the others! A charmingly remodeled Ranch-style home with 4/5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms is situated on an extensive lake view lot. (Only steps from the fishing pier.) You'll adore the versatile, open floor plan design, which is excellent for entertaining or relaxing. This roomy, well-kept property is overflowing with natural light and features gorgeous, vaulted ceilings, granite counters, a dining space, and an island with a breakfast bar. A sizable additional space upstairs can be used as a game room, an additional bedroom, or anything else your heart desires. The magnificent master bedroom is king-sized, spacious, and bright, and the master bathroom has dual vanities, a jacuzzi tub, and an inviting shower. You may entertain in style with the fantastic yard just outside of your home. The neighborhood has a fishing pier, a park, & boat launch. This is the home you've been searching for near the lake!
